Dino Melaye, a former Senator representing Kogi West Senatorial District, has a word for those defecting from the Peoples Democratic Party to the All Progressives Congress.  In an Instagram post he shared, Dino Melaye who was formerly an APC member said the only ”APC man you can trust is the dead APC man.” He Wrote; “Those planing to leave PDP, my humble advise. The only APC man you can trust is the dead Apc man. Don’t be a fool. SDM”  Source